    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入游戏QQ交流群:938700104</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《赛博杀手2049(Cyberkiller 2049)》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是一款平台动作快节奏游戏,在可破坏平台中与众多敌人展开战斗.操纵角色,一击必杀,冲刺,击杀敌人.拾取球棒,遥控炸弹.与拥有不同能力的敌人战斗.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏共设计了三个boss,分别为锤哥,铁血战士和实验体.《赛博杀手2049》希望为玩家带来精彩的boss战.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/d941b5cde4386cb7846ba175e03146c0.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/d941b5cde4386cb7846ba175e03146c0.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/d941b5cde4386cb7846ba175e03146c0.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《赛博杀手2049》有数十种不同机制的敌人,配合游戏中的可破坏墙壁,构成了游戏的核心玩法.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >朋克小子:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单的敌人但也不能掉以轻心.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/24456d7f8383c15232b1c074bbb15c12.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/24456d7f8383c15232b1c074bbb15c12.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/24456d7f8383c15232b1c074bbb15c12.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >棒球小子:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会投掷球棒也能拾取球棒,球棒对玩家造成击倒伤害,近距离近战攻击.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/01e683ca58e73da66b99af1398bd2035.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/01e683ca58e73da66b99af1398bd2035.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/01e683ca58e73da66b99af1398bd2035.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >炸弹小子:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投掷出炸弹,短暂延迟后爆炸造成范围伤害,近距离近战攻击.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/c9676016c4c2e4bab18f6bc6ec9d50ce.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/c9676016c4c2e4bab18f6bc6ec9d50ce.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/c9676016c4c2e4bab18f6bc6ec9d50ce.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >橄榄小子:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可以透过墙壁发现玩家,可破坏路径上的墙壁.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/2e5f9de4a29a74587cc0caadb505c1b8.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/2e5f9de4a29a74587cc0caadb505c1b8.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/2e5f9de4a29a74587cc0caadb505c1b8.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
